<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Nangmah lawng, thangthat, tlak Pathian
 Nangmah lawng, biak tlak mi Pathian
 Cung nungbik, Pathian na si,
 Zeizong te, a ngeitu Pathian, Zeizong te, A uk, tu nasi
 Cu caah, kan in thangthat.

[C1]
   Maw ka nunnak, Bawipa thangthat
   Ka sining, a min thiang, thangthat
   Zeizong vialte a ngeitu cu nangmah na si,
   Bawi vialte, lak ah, cungnungbik
   Nawl ngeitu lak ah, a sang bik
   Nangmah lawng, Pathian na si.

[V2]
 A lianngan, bik mi, Siangpahrang
 A lianngan bik mi, Kan Pathian
 Bawi vialte, lak i Bawi bik
 Caan vialte, A ngei tu, Pathian, Caan vialte, a uk tu na si
 Cu caah, kan in thangthat.</lyrics>
<key>E</key>
<title>NANGMAH LAWNG</title>
</song>